IN SUPPORT
 FOR TEEN PARENTS

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:41.000
AND WHAT THE SCHOOLS
 THEMSELVES CAN DO.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:45.000
Brazelton:
 IT TAKES A LOT OF GUTS TO GO
 BACK TO YOUR FAMILY AND SAY,

