- Narrator:
  "BRAZELTON"...
- SHE NEEDS YOU RIGHT NOW.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:51.000
Narrator:
 "ON PARENTING."

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:13.000
RIGHT NOW OVER A THOUSAND
TEENAGED GIRLS

