FIND THEMSELVES PREGNANT
EVERY DAY IN THIS COUNTRY.

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:18.000
THAT'S AN AMAZING STATISTIC.

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:20.000
AND WE'VE FOUND
THAT TWO THINGS

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:22.000
DETERMINE WHETHER OR NOT
A TEEN MOTHER

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:26.000
WILL BE SUCCESSFUL
IN RAISING HER CHILD:

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:28.000
FIRST, THE SUPPORT
OF HER OWN FAMILY,

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:31.000
AND SECOND, THE SUPPORT
OF HER LARGER FAMILY

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:33.000
OF SCHOOL AND COMMUNITY.

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:36.000
TODAY WE'RE GOING TO LOOK
AT AN EXCITING NEW APPROACH

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:38.000
TO PROVIDING
THAT SUPPORT

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:41.000
AND VISIT WITH SOME
EXTRAORDINARY YOUNG WOMEN

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:44.000
COMMITTED TO BEING
THE BEST PARENTS THEY CAN BE

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:46.000
FOR THEIR BABIES.

00:01:55.000 --> 00:01:57.000
Brazelton:
 LAWRENCE, MASSACHUSETTS,

00:01:57.000 --> 00:02:01.000
- ONE OF AMERICA'S
  OLD INDUSTRIAL CITIES,
- ( bell tolling )

